  "description" : "[h1][url=https://discord.gg/F57ydwPKgz]Discord[/url] | [url=https://github.com/JamesTheMaker/Cosmic-Expanse]GitHub[/url] [/h1]\n\n[b][u]As Cosmic Expanse affects the generation of stars, planets, biomes and more it is recommended to backup and reset your characters and universe before installing![/u][/b]\n\n[h1]About[/h1]\nCosmic Expanse is a full game overhaul that changes and improves upon many vanilla mechanics to create an ultimately more fun and enjoyable game. The mod is far from complete at the moment, with many more planned features to come, so stay tuned!\n\n[h1]Implemented Features[/h1]\n - [b]Full Barren planet rework![/b] Now Barren planets have a purpose, with asteroid-like ore generation!\n - [b]Star/planet generation rework![/b] The universe is a cold and desolate place, so the generation has been changed to reflect this!\n - [b]Dungeon generation rework![/b] No longer will a planet's dungeons be completely random, instead only dungeons relevant to the planet type will spawn on it's surface!\n\n[h1]Planned/WIP Features[/h1]\n - [b]Powered machinery![/b] From grinders to maximize your ore output to growing trays for your modern farm, Cosmic Expanse will have all the machines you need! (at the small cost of some power)\n - [b]BYOS/BYOSS system![/b] Your imagination will run wild with unparalleled customization on your ships and space stations!\n - [b]New planet types![/b] Mountanous, fleshy, swamp, tar and many more unique worlds to come!\n - [b]Expanded lore![/b] Cosmic Expanse will flesh out the simple and lackluster lore of Starbound with many new interesting codices, NPCs and dungeons!\n - [b]And much more![/b]",
